	   <tr><td colspan=2>Focus items at pre 34th level.<br><br>Many people argue whether the focus items work below lvl 34.<br>I have done some testing with lvl 20 water pets that (at least for me conclusively) shows an effect.<br><br>I tested a lvl 20 water pet, with and without burnout, against another lvl 20 water pet of the same level and received the following stats.<br>- with burnout<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;My pet always won with about 15-25% hits remaining. This was done 5 times.<br>- without burnout<br>  My pet always won with about 10-20% hits remaining. This was done 4 times.<br><br>These 10% to 25% means the pet will last a few rounds more, so its not a huge advantage, which i suppose it will be at lvl 34.<br><br>The size is also quite a bit larger (about 70% larger.<br><br>Good luck and take care,<br>Ethelwind, Mage of 23rd rank.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
