	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have used Water Pets (almost) exclusively to lvl 33. There are a number of reasons for this ...<br><br>1. As an Erudite I follow Prexus (sea god) - so there's a kinda Role-playing side to it<br><br>2. They kick ass. Earth pet has more muscle, but the Water pet's DD keeps pace with the damage.<br><br>3. Their regen really helps my down-time.<br><br>4. Only having to research one line of pets, helps a lot - financially, and in hunting out those elusive words etc.<br><br>5.The top pet in the game is a water pet.<br><br>Nuff said?<br><br>Marm Ageddon<br>lvl 33 Mage on Inoruuk<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
