	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Aug 18th 11:05 AM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.71]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Once you reach level eight you should get a bind in Qeynos and travel to BB.&nbsp;&nbsp;Before you go in you should download a map, BB can be confusing.  Cast invis and travel to the snake ledge, ask someone to guide you if you don't know where it is.  Four giant snakes spawn on this ledge close together.  Don't worry, they won't gang up on you.  Cast you pet, tell it to guard somewhere on the ledge so it won't wander and pull a guardsman or two.  Killing the snakes is easy, just cast a Shock of Blades and let you pet tank.  Cast one more shock and constantly monitor your pet's health.  Cast another shock or bolt and when your pets health is below 35% start tanking for it.  If you have to cast another DD.  Once the snake dies, med and bind your wounds if you need to, then take another snake.  The snakes drop fangs and venom sacks which sell for 4 gold each.  Be careful the fangs weigh alot, you don't want to be walking back and be jumped by a guardsman and his buddies.  Don't worry if BB is crowded, 9 out of 10 times there will not be anyone on the ledge.  Hope this helps.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
