	   <tr><td colspan=2>You can also use a trick to get to the snakes fast.&nbsp;&nbsp;Enter BB and go to the tree with the trap in the bottom.  Cast invs on yourself and then drop through the pit into the water below. Climb out and move down the hall. Check you invs then go left and though the door into the spike room.  Go down the ramp in the spike room and up the other side.  Go out the door and to the right, at the bottom of the passage is the snake ledge.<br><br>Take the poster above's advice and get a map. It makes it clearer.  Also, you can gate out when you are done and not have to worry about getting around the dungeon.<br><br>Cetus<br>The Nameless<br>&nbsp;<br>Cetus<br>The Nameless</td></tr>
