	   <tr><td colspan=2>this post is meant to help the soloing magician.<br>this works in groups but is probly of very little value in a group.<br><br>First cast a pet (earth or a focused water) and flame shield it. NOTE: don't think you are saving mana with a fire pet you really only waste mana in the long run.<br>Send the pet in. target pet and med. keep an eye on your pets health. only it gets to around 30% stand up and type /pet get lost. DON"T HIT ENTER YET! begin to recast your pet and when the spell is almost done hit enter TA DA you have a new pet. flame shield and repeat. NOTE: don't be tempted to heal your pet unless you are below 16 at which point this strategy shouldn't be used anyway. Nuking is ok as long as you have still have enough mana for a new pet.<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Speel Lavamaster<br>magician , monk , and warrior extrodinaire.<br></td></tr>
