	   <tr><td colspan=2>well i just thought i would say something about healing the pet. <br><br>What i meant was this around 24-25 healing the pet and nuking becomes riskier because the best heal you have is for 200hp and mobs are hitting for 55+ multiple times a round which makes heals less useful.<br><br>I personally used the pet heal method. i used a fire pet at 24 and by just healing i could solo Yellow and red gnolls outside SP in SK. <br><br>i used fire pet because a little known fact is that the damage shield it has is much stronger then anything we can cast. fire pets shield is (level+1)damage. so at 24 your pet has a 23 point fire shield and if you can keep it healed things die very quickly. again though this strategy will probly not work in the 30's simply because mobs hit harder and faster then you can heal and a dead pet means a long corpse recovery.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
