	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hello all!<br><br>I am Naeluuven a 15th level mage on the Xegony server (i had a 20th mage but i deleted him)<br><br>Ok this guide will be about soloing from lvl 4 to 16 =)<br><br>Now first thing you must do is get yourself over to steamfont mountains,(make sure to be stocked up on malachite!)once there, you need to find the first kobold camp,say that its camped,and get ready for some fun! (if it is camped you can take the one on the hill or the spiderlings and clockworks)First make sure you bought bandages the water pet spell (or earth pet,i prefer water but earth isnt bad either)your ae spell,summon food/drink,and a nuke (if you cant offored these spells i suggest the food/water, a pet,fire flux,and invis)<br><br>Time to fight!!!<br>now after you have food and drink,a good pet,and are shielded with full mana (fm for short,) get ready to bust up some kobolds,<br>First strategy for kobolds is to always take out the con yellow or the shaman ALWAYS focus on these(its also a good idea to be bound in akanon right where you zone in,its a blind spot for the npcs there)now once you have nuked put your pet into the fray,now once he is at 70 hp join him with the ae ready and keep doing this till all the kobolds are dead,rest,repeat till your lvl 7 (note at lvl 6 let other people join and say they can have what cons green to you). now at lvl 7 solo by the mino caves or windmills (try to not to fight the rats and big colckworks, AND STAY AWAY FROM THE SKELETONS!!!!)once you get lvl 8 mem invis,(you did buy that from neriak right =))cast it, and head home! (refresh invis whene needed)you should have gotten a fair amount of cash from those drakes and kobolds,so once home buy a water pet,your new nukes,dmg shield if you get one at 8 (i forgot hehe) and a summon weapon spell, and gate back to Akanon.<br><br>Ahhh new nukes how wonderful,use shock of blades instead of the fire based one (forgot name)it has a faster casting time for less mana and is resisted less,go to east/west commons and kill spiders and stuff that cons black/yellow/blue.<br><br>Once you get lvl 10 go to freeport get a bind at the docks,get on the boat and once you zone into oot (ocean of tears)you will see an island with a dock, and a penenusela that looks like florida,jump off at the penenusela and summon a pet,kill sisters till lvl 12 gate back to fp and head home.<br><br>Get your spells,and head to the desert of northern ro for some dervs,bind at the tunnel,facing the desert,and get in a camp 5 or wall camp group (dorns camp may also work but its dangerous he can be indifferent one second and thene bs you for 120 the other)once you get lvl 14 from dervs (the exp comes quik, trust me)head to oasis and kill dw caimens,regular crocs and caimens and giant spiders/madmen (you can also do the orc camp 1,you can get there by heading along the beach keeping the ocean to your left heading from north ro)till you get lvl 16,go home to get your spells and i think by now you can fnd a place to hunt on your own.<br><br>Notes:<br>Bind at the far end of the docks in oasis.<br><br>Make sure to get 3 back packs and the dimensional pocket spell before going to sister island,fill the pockets with halberds and the packs with belts/words/runes.<br><br>You can sell to Pardor the blessed in commons (hes in the middle hut on the left facing west commons).<br><br>Work on tailoring as soon as possible,you can make raw silk to wear, sell or both with the spider silks off giant spiders.<br><br>Sorry that i didnt go up to 20 i will add that once im there, again,and theres a certain spawn i camp from 16-20 that i didnt want to give away till i am done with it,i will probebly add it once i get there.<br><br>Have fun,<br>Naeluuven 15th mage of the Xegony server.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
